javax.jaxtx.acid
Interface Vote

public interface Vote

This enumeration represents the possible vote results that a participant can return from prepare.

Version:
$Id: Vote.java,v 1.1 2004/06/22 10:07:57 nmcl Exp $

Field Summary
static int COMMIT
          The participant has determined that it can commit.
static int READ_ONLY
          The participant does not manage any modified state on behalf of the transaction, so it does not need to participant in the second phase of the commit protocol (whether that it to commit or roll back).
static int ROLLBACK
          The participant has determined that it cannot commit and so will force the transaction to roll back.
